In [15]:
subset_columns = ['DailyAverageRelativeHumidity', 'DailyPrecipitation', 'DailyAverageWindSpeed']
subset_data = data[subset_columns]


subset_data = subset_data.dropna()


sns.pairplot(subset_data)
plt.suptitle('Pair Plot of Selected Climate Variables', y=1.02)
plt.show()
In [18]:
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 10))
ax = plt.subplot(1, 1, 1, polar=True)
ax.set_theta_offset(math.pi / 2)
ax.set_theta_direction(-1)
ax.set_rlabel_position(0)


data['DailySustainedWindDirectionRad'] = data['DailySustainedWindDirection'] * (math.pi / 180)


ax.hist(data['DailySustainedWindDirectionRad'].dropna(), bins=36, color='skyblue', edgecolor='black')
ax.set_title('Wind Rose Plot for Sustained Wind Direction')
plt.show()

data['DailyPrecipitation'] = pd.to_numeric(data['DailyPrecipitation'], errors='coerce')
plt.figure(figsize=(10, 6))
sns.histplot(data['DailyPrecipitation'].dropna(), bins=30, kde=True)
plt.title('Daily Precipitation Distribution')
plt.xlabel('Daily Precipitation (mm)')
plt.ylabel('Frequency')
plt.show()
